            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Закодируй переменную, которая отображает <code>\"Take an umbrella\"</code> в консоли.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"is_rainy = \" /><text value=\"True\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"is_sunny = \" /><text value=\"False\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" is_rainy:\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Take an umbrella&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"36\" endIndex=\"44\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"is_sunny\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Take an umbrella\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>is_rainy</code>.</p></body></html>"
